5都冇一樣冇問題<br />\n個樣生得安全就唔驚啦"},{"pid":"c66191f00aee764c4a7585ec33678d30905d6609","tid":618354,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c8ee36cc01fdcac6428f13b2840e720d74ba26","tid":618354,"uid":82184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"18歲自己一個去台灣，但都唔係好算旅行嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去跑馬拉松但留咗3日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:53:45.000Z","msg":"我19歲自己一個去左25日台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ad55108e41cc5dd72fc8fc09cd9fcc4391ea9b","tid":618354,"uid":154533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:56:35.000Z","msg":"15歲自己坐火車去桂林 <br />\n不過果邊係有人接應晚"},{"pid":"7530f57b720c6cbad9692752880992c7660531f3","tid":618354,"uid":96135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"21歲 自己一個去左日本玩左8日<br />\n買左張jr pass周圍去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd24a12184d0bb4627b0214722e12ff0d68cc8c","tid":618354,"uid":165786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:59:14.000Z","msg":"22歲 第一次係去法國第二次去比利時 其實日本已經算安全喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30032930c807252ceef6da9be54fce7188a52c62","tid":618354,"uid":180719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:59:43.000Z","msg":"19歲去左英國兩個星期玩到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1582c731d71acc00812232ee5a599593a649d618","tid":618354,"uid":156807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"20歲仔單拖遊英國2星期 全程都係住Hostel 識下hostel啲人玩 之後都自己去過幾轉台灣"},{"pid":"d6c24a41c470dfb06650573bce17d48c7f980bcb","tid":618354,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:02:14.000Z","msg":"21歲去英國4個月<br />\n上年去日本3個月,唔識日文都冇問題"},{"pid":"4e59d6cf79fd6e556ee5e1db1cd3611c34f15fbc","tid":618354,"uid":107950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:03:27.000Z","msg":"20歲自己一個去台灣，住Hostel識朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本勁安全，放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋唔太識日文無問題，用簡單英文溝通到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dec8b5f3ed61bac0979de830869c4c67b9083d3","tid":618354,"uid":122373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:04:12.000Z","msg":"20歲 東京<br />\n語言絕對唔係問題 我當時除左廣東話同中文就同聾啞文盲冇咩分別 一樣冇穿冇爛返到嚟"},{"pid":"33712187022893de80974d7db58f2db230bf05e8","tid":618354,"uid":138265,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"354190469f500aba7b1d75f19ad5271eb140b5a2","tid":618354,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:51:54.000Z","msg":"考完dse 先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:06:38.000Z","msg":"我大學yr 1啦"},{"pid":"2c40d60fd4e21488578be8b21c2f4a2108aef4d0","tid":618354,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:08:15.000Z","msg":"22 澳洲+紐西蘭 差唔多4 個月"},{"pid":"02a3dc84ce63f2aab98b6d09965d27052e5dd56c","tid":618354,"uid":138265,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:11:07.000Z","msg":"睇落大家都係2字頭先自己一個去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實上嚟問嘅主要原因係今次係去見日本網友，搵佢玩下。<br />\n但怕日本多痴線佬，等陣俾佢開始後庭咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係去打算去7-10日"},{"pid":"f77aad0a352fed3d7e6763423b46030f7230cc25","tid":618354,"uid":138265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c66191f00aee764c4a7585ec33678d30905d6609","tid":618354,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c8ee36cc01fdcac6428f13b2840e720d74ba26","tid":618354,"uid":82184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"1