:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"20歲 去左50日歐洲"},{"pid":"2b851385c10dc4119766dcb7868d84f7991c98b1","tid":618354,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:42:04.000Z","msg":"17歲去咗東京一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw有日文底"},{"pid":"7ccba89efb2f6dc9692e744ff4436158842556e4","tid":618354,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"東京都驚安全？<br />\n去邊忽？"},{"pid":"8e5818cc364f35b3c160204953e9ea2715d8ee20","tid":618354,"uid":54326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"試過台灣 好多台妹撩你傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n專去啲鄉下地方睇下風景 唔係嘅話好似出左旺角咁 周街都香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e97f2f57aef22169b531784742ef61d00e062d","tid":618354,"uid":68078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"第一次獨遊係大學 year 3 去新加坡 諗住最安全<br />\n結果安全到買手信漏低咗銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾個鐘後都拎得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後獨遊過東京 台北 最近去完英國<br />\n<br />\n其實一條友去旅行真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人有計劃得嚟又好 last minute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我通常係 mark 曬一堆想去嘅地方<br />\n每一晚就 plan 定下一兩日嘅行程<br />\n每日行程預鬆少少 如果太早完成又可以臨時去多個地方咁<br />\n食咩行咩坐咩睇咩就自己心情就得<br />\n係食嘢麻煩啲 同埋少個照應咁解囉<br />\n(自問依家獨遊過嘅地方都唔算危險 最危可能就係英遊期間去咗一日巴黎)"},{"pid":"e23fb4c4884c2a4f7383a4efd91a0c250e013e7c","tid":618354,"uid":68078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e97f2f57aef22169b531784742ef61d00e062d","tid":618354,"uid":68078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"第一次獨遊係大學 year 3 去新加坡 諗住最安全<br />\n結果安全到買手信漏低咗銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla